Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish of Chester. 
    See also Table 2, notes (a) and (g).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parishes of Burton, 
    Ellesmere Port, Ness, Neston cum Parkgate and Willaston. Renamed 21.6.1976 
    to become the Ellesmere Port & Neston unparished area. See also Table 2, note 
    (c).

Unparished area created 21.6.1976 by renaming the Ellesmere Port 
    unparished area. See also Table 2, notes (e), (f) and (g).

Created 1.4.1987 out of the Ellesmere Port & Neston unparished 
    area. See also Table 2, note (g).
